{"tid":1827680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"25歲仔旺角遭4刀手追斬   身中多刀見骨命危    防暴警冇影","createTime":"2020-01-17T06:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T07:06:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ce033177adaa6cc69d8580ebe3179e7baa5c30f5","tid":1827680,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:46:57.000Z","msg":"【13:25】事主經治療後仍然危殆，留醫廣華醫院。<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n旺角西洋菜南街發生斬人血案！昨晚(16日)11時許，一名25歲姓董男子，途經兆萬中心對開時，突然遭4名手持利刀、戴口罩男子施襲，事主見狀拔足逃走，惟仍被刀手追及狂斬多刀，左膝傷口深至見骨，而右後腹被斬開見內臟，事主受傷昏迷倒臥血泊中，現場留有大攤血漬，多名途人見狀報警，4名刀手逞兇後跑至數十米外，並登上泊於登打士街的一輛七人車，逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n救護員到場將傷者送院搶救，警方圍封現場，地上遺下一攤恐怖血漬，而兇徒所乘的七人車停泊位置地上，發現一個相信是屬於兇徒的口罩。經調查後，案件列傷人，交旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。警方正追查兇徒犯案動機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200117/photo/bkn-20200117005537812-0117_00822_001_04b.jpg?20200117135347\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200117005537812-0117_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20200117135347&h=d7b63684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200117/bkn-20200117005537812-0117_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3ee193ed5ab4ba4a4ddf51a640ff46461912bb9a","tid":1827680,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借一個位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<br />\n今日好多響task2呀 <br />\n幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcygy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=e9378d6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<spa